messages.content: Hello there! It's so nice to meet you. How can I help make your day even better?
haha tell me something to do

I'm glad you're enjoying our conversation! Since you mentioned wanting to try something new, why don't we play a game of 20 Questions? I'll think of 20 interesting or fun questions for you to answer about yourself. Let's start!
1. What's your favorite color?
2. If you could live anywhere in the world, where would it be?
3. What's your most cherished memory?
4. What's your go-to ice cream flavor?
5. Have you ever had a pet? If so, what kind and what was their name?
6. What's the best book you've ever read?
7. If you could learn to speak any language fluently, which one would it be?
8. What's the most adventurous thing you've ever done?
9. What's your favorite type of food or cuisine?
10. What's something that makes you laugh or smile?
11. What's the best concert or live performance you've ever attended?
12. If you could have dinner with any historical figure, who would it be and why?
13. What's the most beautiful place you've ever seen?
14. What's your favorite type of weather?
15. What's something that scares you a little bit?
16. What's the best advice you've ever received?
17. If you could have any superpower, which one would it be and why?
18. What's your proudest accomplishment?
19. What's something you're really looking forward to in the future?
20. What's something people might not know about you?
